{"title":"万紫千红最称心","authors":["放平"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":1,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"万紫千红最称心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日高照红旗升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进锣鼓迎新春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家门前红灯亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人脸上笑盈盈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公共食堂排盛宴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼肉饺子香喷喷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千城万社多热闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共举酒杯把酒斟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一杯胜利酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满满地斟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们跟着您！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您是红日当空照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得全国都是春！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二杯胜利酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满满地斟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着亲爱的党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们表决心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党是咱们的亲父母，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们和党一条心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三杯胜利酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满满地斟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们高声唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱出英雄的心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高声歌唱共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高声歌唱大跃进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日高照红旗升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进锣鼓迎新春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎新春，鼓干劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万紫千红最称心！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}